author: kfogel
msg: Follow up to r12774: Restore the SVN_CL__TRY macro and use it to skip
unversioned resources, but make it set a boolean success indicator, so
callers can know whether or not to do notification.
(SVN_CL__TRY): Restored, but now with a boolean success indicator.
(svn_cl__propset): Use SVN_CL__TRY instead of writing it out by hand.
(svn_cl__propdel): Use SVN_CL__TRY instead of writing it out by hand.
